    {
      "chinese": "他們也一起去山上狩獵，因小矮人的體格較矮小，只能獵取較小的獵物，例如兔子、小鳥、飛鼠等等；賽德克族比較會獵取山羌、山羊、山豬及水鹿等等。他們每次狩獵時打到的獵物各不同，大小也不一樣，回到家之後，家人認為肉分的不公平，而不太高興。",
      "ab": "Ida mseupu musa tmsamac lmiqu uri ka dhiya, biciq hniygan seejiq ga, mkla balay tmsamac, yasa biciq hniygan dha kika snegaaw biciq ssamac ka nnangal dha, saw ka sbirac, qduda, rapic dnii. Seejiq Balay o snegaaw paru ssamac ka nnangal dha, saw ka pada, miric, rqnux ni bowyak dnii. Kiya ni dhuq sapah do yasa kiya nanaq ka napa dha maku marih ka tnsapah biciq hniygan seejiq wah!",
      "order": "2",
